name: Liberty 2009
additionalNotes:
Only 40,000 cigars were produced.

The Liberty 2009 is a 6" x 56 figurado. The 2009 was blended by Christian Eiroa. Utilizing Camacho’s only ever Habano crop of tobacco, the ’09 is a rich, complex medium-full bodied blend, which has been patiently aging since they were rolled in 2007.
